description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Napping in a bed of fallen leaves
-Two kittens with blue eyes
-Kitten surrounded by hydrangeas
-Kittens asleep in a blanket
-Balls of yarn and kittens
-Kitten playing in mirror
-Sleeping on yarn balls
-Six kittens in cups
-Two kittens playing outside
-Sleep on a fluffy blanket
name: Sweet Kittens
